                <note rend="inline" type="source">865.6363/3–345: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kirk</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-03-09T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >March 9, 1945—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>474. Reurtel 590, March 3, 10 a.m. Department concurs that note be presented
                    after publication of decree.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
